ResponseBody:
WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Skills and Abilities

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Batman has no inherent superpowers.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:11.000
He relies on his own scientific knowledge, detective skills, and athletic prowess.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:15.000
In the stories, Batman is regarded as one of the world's greatest detectives,

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.000
if not the world's greatest crime solver.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Batman has been repeatedly described as having genius-level intellect,

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:26.000
one of the greatest martial artists in the DC universe,

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.000
and having peak human physical conditioning.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:34.000
He has traveled the world acquiring the skills needed to aid his crusade against crime.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:39.000
His knowledge and expertise in almost every discipline known to man

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:43.000
is nearly unparalleled by any other character in the universe.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Batman's inexhaustible wealth allows him to access advanced technology.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:54.000
As a proficient scientist, he is able to use and modify those technologies to his advantage.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Batman describes Superman as the most dangerous man on Earth,

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:06.000
able to defeat a team of super-powered extraterrestrials by himself

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:12.000
in order to rescue his imprisoned teammates in the first storyline.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Superman also considers Batman to be one of the most brilliant minds on the planet.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:22.000
Batman has the ability to function under great physical pain

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:25.000
and withstand mind control.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:30.000
He is a master of disguise, multilingual, and an expert in espionage,

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:35.000
often gathering information under different identities.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:44.000
Batman's karate, judo, and jiu-jitsu training has made him a master of stealth and escape,

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:52.000
allowing him to appear and disappear at will, and to break free from his prison.
